<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٣٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَنْقُلُ وَيَقُولُ: لَوْلَا أَنْتَ مَا اهْتَدَيْنَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>